name: ME vs ME YOU vs ME

metadata.name: ME vs ME, YOU vs YOU
metadata.description:
I have the ability to create my own happiness 
I can never be you and you can never be me
Your judgements doesn't really matter to me because you're judging me based on what you think about me

Again, I can never be you and you can never be me
I control my emotions and my feelings 
I am my own competition 
The only person competing with me is Me

ME vs ME  YOU vs YOU
